903
00:51:32,701 --> 00:51:33,701
Socials.

904
00:51:35,141 --> 00:51:36,141
Goldmine.

905
00:51:36,941 --> 00:51:38,261
I am so proud of you.

906
00:51:38,901 --> 00:51:39,901
Yeah.

907
00:51:42,061 --> 00:51:44,581
