941
00:54:07,261 --> 00:54:08,261
[grunts]

942
00:54:09,661 --> 00:54:10,661
[grunts]

943
00:54:11,581 --> 00:54:12,581
[grunts]

944
00:54:18,261 --> 00:54:19,781
[laughs]

945
00:54:28,221 --> 00:54:30,541
[laughs]

946
00:54:33,621 --> 00:54:35,141
May your beer always be cold.

947
00:54:35,221 --> 00:54:36,581
[laughs]

948
00:54:38,621 --> 00:54:40,941
May your boys always be hot.

949
00:54:42,941 --> 00:54:45,581
- Come hell or high water.
- It is you and me.

950
00:54:46,461 --> 00:54:47,901
No matter what.

951
00:54:47,941 --> 00:54:49,101
No matter what.

952
00:54:51,541 --> 00:54:54,581
[somber music continues]

953
00:54:55,221 --> 00:54:56,221
Cheers.

954
00:55:01,261 --> 00:55:02,261
