that you could have known.

990
00:58:43,541 --> 00:58:44,621
And there's...

991
00:58:45,581 --> 00:58:47,821
there's no one else that
I'd rather be stuck on this,

992
00:58:48,781 --> 00:58:51,181
shitty, shitty rock with.

993
00:58:51,861 --> 00:58:52,941
[chuckles]

994
