1003
00:59:27,821 --> 00:59:28,941
No, I covered for you.

1004
00:59:29,461 --> 00:59:31,501
Said you're at home practicing your cello.

1005
00:59:33,421 --> 00:59:35,141
[Trish] The guy was
someone I used to work with and

1006
00:59:35,221 --> 00:59:37,421
